rComments: I currently am in Professor Vassiliou's class (Pol 200 - Political theory). He's so cool! He looks so young, but his mind is just flooded with intellect. He was very caring when I requested an extension. Lectures are interesting and funny, though very heavy. He always engages with the class to make it exciting. Thanks to him, my summer is great.

TA for 200 (orwin) and pol101 and totally loved the classes and understood more about the material. made political theory so much more bearable and simplified the stuff enough to help learn it without destroying the essential complexity of the texts. really helped understand the assignment. regret not taking the course with him in the summer tho
Legend. Absolute legend. The most insightful, engaging, and approachable Instructor I have had to date.
